ss=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">23 July</span> 2013</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Epoch+Times&amp;rft.atitle=Cuban+%27rafters%27+Commemorate+Tugboat+Massacre&amp;rft.aulast=McLennan&amp;rft.aufirst=Pam&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.theepochtimes.com%2Fn2%2Fcanada%2Fcuban-remember-tugboat-massacre-19571.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ATugboat+%2213+de+Marzo%22+massacre\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_links\">External links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Tugboat_%2213_de_Marzo%22_massacre&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: External links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20030515130109/http://web.amnesty.org/library/Index/ENGAMR250131997?open&amp;of=ENG-CUB\">Amnesty International report</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.fiu.edu/~fcf/OAS-Castillo/oas.13march.reportcast697.html\">Inter-American Court of Human Rights report on the incident</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cubaverdad.net/13_de_marzo.htm\">Links to various reports and Newsfeeds</a></li></ul>\n<p><span id=\"coordinates\" class=\"metadata coord-missing\"></span>\n</p>\n<div role=\"navigation\" class=\"navbox\" aria-labelledby=\"Shipwrecks_and_maritime_incidents_in_1994\" style=\"padding:3px\"><table class=\"nowraplinks collapsible collapsed navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;color:inherit\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist navbar mini\"><ul><l